  "course_description": "This course helps students learn and apply practical frameworks and systematic processes for addressing complex, real-world problems and facilitating effective action. It helps solidify an enterprise view by integrating across the lessons and tools of multiple Core courses. It bridges the ideas of the classroom and the practical actions and complications of the real world - and especially the challenges of team-based projects, which define much of the post-MBA work environment. Students work in teams to apply a structured approach to problem solving that gives problem owners the clarity and confidence to take action.",
